## 🔧 Useful UFW Commands

### List rules with numbers (for deletion)
```bash
sudo ufw status numbered
```

### Delete a rule by number
```bash
sudo ufw delete 2
```

### Reset all rules (start over)
```bash
sudo ufw reset
# Then re-add the rules you want
```

### Disable UFW entirely
```bash
sudo ufw disable
```

### See what's blocked (logs)
```bash
sudo ufw logging on   # turn on logging
sudo tail -f /var/log/ufw.log
```

